#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`/q/health`"
msgstr "`/q/健康`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`/q/metrics`"
msgstr "`/q/metrics`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`/q/openapi`"
msgstr "`/q/openapi`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`/q/info`"
msgstr "`/q/info`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "but users can also choose to expose one that might present a security risk under a different TCP port using a dedicated xref:management-interface-reference.adoc[management interface]."
msgstr "但用户也可以选择通过专用 xref:management-interface-reference.adoc[管理接口] ，将可能存在安全风险的端口映射到另一个TCP端口上。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Info endpoint"
msgstr "信息端点"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the application contains the `quarkus-info` extension, then Quarkus will by default expose the `/q/info` endpoint which provides information about the build, java version, version control, and operating system. The level of detail of the exposed information is configurable."
msgstr "如果应用程序包含 `quarkus-info` 扩展，那么 Quarkus 将默认暴露 `/q/info` 端点，该端点提供有关构建、Java 版本、版本控制和操作系统的信息。所暴露信息的详细程度是可以配置的。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "All CDI beans implementing the `InfoContributor` will be picked up and their data will be appended to the endpoint."
msgstr "所有实现 `InfoContributor` 接口的 CDI Bean 都会被识别出来，其数据将被追加到端点中。"

